movie.title: Stan & Ollie
movie.plot: With their golden era long behind them, comedy duo Stan Laurel and Oliver Hardy embark on a variety hall tour of Britain and Ireland. Despite the pressures of a hectic schedule, and with the support of their wives Lucille and Ida – a formidable double act in their own right – the pair's love of performing, as well as for each other, endures as they secure their place in the hearts of their adoring public
movie.awards: Nominated for 1 Golden Globe. Another 5 wins & 25 nominations.
